{"tid":1243592,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱食飯有條女讚我嗰度長，於是我就俾佢摸下","createTime":"2019-06-19T13:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T18:01:03.000Z","uid":150100,"like":27,"dislike":420,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9a80345753787c75e1be6dced684e7234d9f27f5","tid":1243592,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:56:04.000Z","msg":"話說頭先自己一個喺譚仔食飯啦<br />\n咁我都係照平時咁連登撈飯啦<br />\n<br />\n點知突然有個女仔行埋嚟<br />\n嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你個咩好長吖！<br />\n<br />\n我嗰下都覺得好尷尬，點知佢之後嗰句仲爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我可唔可拎上手摸下吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係講笑<br />\n我咁大個仔，波都揸過，但係都未遇過啲咁進取嘅女仔<br />\n我望一望佢，見佢都算係五官標緻<br />\n我一個血氣方剛嘅成年男人仲點忍得住<br />\n但係依度話曬都係大庭廣眾<br />\n依啲野始終唔係咁方便<br />\n<br />\n於是我拿拿林埋單<br />\n帶個女仔飛的去半島<br />\n入到房鎖好門熄埋燈<br />\n我就拎出嚟放喺佢手上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗱，依部就係Sony Xperia 1喇"},{"pid":"495dc640cb19b50dea0740db99a9b677aa1743fc","tid":1243592,"uid":150100,"like":214,"dislike":5,"score":209,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UrnjDVh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUrnjDVh.jpg&h=cab18d65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b18fd8cea1c674927302c49e6728f59450e249e2","tid":1243592,"uid":6195,"like":137,"dislike":0,"score":137,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:57:11.000Z","msg":"譚仔食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630cb22b4cd32d20110169f6583a5d2405f8454e","tid":1243592,"uid":150100,"like":48,"dislike":2,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:57:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b0H7NOO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb0H7NOO.png&h=0432ae78&